{
  "video_id": "jAw8t2g-eVU",
  "title": "How to motivate people to do good for others | Erez Yoeli",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13440.0,
      "end_time": 16496.0,
      "text": "How can we get people to do more good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16520.0,
      "end_time": 20856.0,
      "text": "to go to the polls, give to charity, conserve resources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20880.0,
      "end_time": 24215.0,
      "text": "or even to do something as simple as washing their mugs at work"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24240.0,
      "end_time": 26621.0,
      "text": "so that the sink isn&#39;t always full of dirty dishes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26645.0,
      "end_time": 28656.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28680.0,
      "end_time": 33160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33400.0,
      "end_time": 35176.0,
      "text": "When I first started working on this problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35200.0,
      "end_time": 37960.0,
      "text": "I collaborated with a power company"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37120.0,
      "end_time": 40656.0,
      "text": "to recruit customers for a program that prevents blackouts"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40680.0,
      "end_time": 42680.0,
      "text": "by reducing energy demand during peaks."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43600.0,
      "end_time": 46216.0,
      "text": "The program is based on a tried-and-true technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46240.0,
      "end_time": 48616.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s one the Obama administration even called"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48640.0,
      "end_time": 51760.0,
      "text": "\"the cornerstone to modernizing America&#39;s electrical grid.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52880.0,
      "end_time": 56376.0,
      "text": "But, like so many great technological solutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56400.0,
      "end_time": 57839.0,
      "text": "it has a key weakness:"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59760.0,
      "end_time": 60960.0,
      "text": "people."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61720.0,
      "end_time": 62960.0,
      "text": "People need to sign up."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64000.0,
      "end_time": 67536.0,
      "text": "To try to get people to sign up, the power company sent them a nice letter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67560.0,
      "end_time": 69576.0,
      "text": "told them about all the program&#39;s benefits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69600.0,
      "end_time": 72655.0,
      "text": "and it asked them to call into a hotline if they were interested."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72680.0,
      "end_time": 74376.0,
      "text": "Those letters went out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74400.0,
      "end_time": 77160.0,
      "text": "but the phones, they were silent."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78800.0,
      "end_time": 80840.0,
      "text": "So when we got involved, we suggested one small change."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81360.0,
      "end_time": 83256.0,
      "text": "Instead of that hotline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83280.0,
      "end_time": 87896.0,
      "text": "we suggested that they use sign-up sheets that they&#39;d post near the mailboxes"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87920.0,
      "end_time": 89160.0,
      "text": "in people&#39;s buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90120.0,
      "end_time": 92880.0,
      "text": "This tripled participation."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95160.0,
      "end_time": 96360.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97680.0,
      "end_time": 101896.0,
      "text": "Well, we all know people care deeply about what others think of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101920.0,
      "end_time": 104576.0,
      "text": "that we try to be seen as generous and kind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104600.0,
      "end_time": 107320.0,
      "text": "and we try to avoid being seen as selfish or a mooch."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108120.0,
      "end_time": 112536.0,
      "text": "Whether we are aware of it or not, this is a big part of why people do good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 112560.0,
      "end_time": 117776.0,
      "text": "and so small changes that give people more credit for doing good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117800.0,
      "end_time": 120136.0,
      "text": "those changes can make a really big difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 120160.0,
      "end_time": 123560.0,
      "text": "Small changes like switching from a hotline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123800.0,
      "end_time": 126960.0,
      "text": "where nobody will ever find out about your good deed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 126120.0,
      "end_time": 127856.0,
      "text": "to a sign-up sheet"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127880.0,
      "end_time": 131000.0,
      "text": "where anyone who walks by can see your name."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132520.0,
      "end_time": 135696.0,
      "text": "In our collaborations with governments, nonprofits, companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135720.0,
      "end_time": 138536.0,
      "text": "when we&#39;re trying to get people to do more good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138560.0,
      "end_time": 140960.0,
      "text": "we harness the power of reputations."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 142000.0,
      "end_time": 144376.0,
      "text": "And we have a simple checklist for this."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 144400.0,
      "end_time": 147640.0,
      "text": "And in fact, you already know the first item on that checklist."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 148960.0,
      "end_time": 151256.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s to increase observability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 151280.0,
      "end_time": 154000.0,
      "text": "to make sure people find out about good deeds."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 155440.0,
      "end_time": 158335.0,
      "text": "Now, wait a minute, I know some of you are probably thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158360.0,
      "end_time": 160560.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no way people here thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 160800.0,
      "end_time": 162736.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, well, now that I&#39;m getting credit for my good deed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 162760.0,
      "end_time": 164960.0,
      "text": "now it&#39;s totally worth it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 164120.0,
      "end_time": 165576.0,
      "text": "And you&#39;re right."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165600.0,
      "end_time": 166840.0,
      "text": "Usually, people don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167760.0,
      "end_time": 170816.0,
      "text": "Rather, when they&#39;re making decisions in private,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170840.0,
      "end_time": 172576.0,
      "text": "they worry about their own problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 172600.0,
      "end_time": 176736.0,
      "text": "about what to put on the table for dinner or how to pay their bills on time."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176760.0,
      "end_time": 179856.0,
      "text": "But, when we make their decision more observable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 179880.0,
      "end_time": 182960.0,
      "text": "they start to attend more to the opportunity to do good."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 183760.0,
      "end_time": 186576.0,
      "text": "In other words, what&#39;s so powerful about our approach"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 186600.0,
      "end_time": 191456.0,
      "text": "is that it could turn on people&#39;s existing desire to do good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 191480.0,
      "end_time": 193560.0,
      "text": "in this case, to help to prevent a blackout."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 195160.0,
      "end_time": 196816.0,
      "text": "Back to observability."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 196840.0,
      "end_time": 198696.0,
      "text": "I want to give you another example."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 198720.0,
      "end_time": 200456.0,
      "text": "This one is from a collaboration"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 200480.0,
      "end_time": 202856.0,
      "text": "with a nonprofit that gets out the vote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 202880.0,
      "end_time": 206456.0,
      "text": "and it does this by sending hundreds of thousands of letters every election"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 206480.0,
      "end_time": 209799.0,
      "text": "in order to remind people and try to motivate them to go to the polls."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 210760.0,
      "end_time": 212920.0,
      "text": "We suggested adding the following sentence:"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 214440.0,
      "end_time": 217840.0,
      "text": "\"Someone may call you to find out about your experience at the polls.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 218520.0,
      "end_time": 221920.0,
      "text": "This sentence makes it feel more observable when you go to the polls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223400.0,
      "end_time": 226790.0,
      "text": "and it increased the effect of the letter by 50 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 228680.0,
      "end_time": 232416.0,
      "text": "Making the letter more effective reduced the cost of getting an additional vote"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 232440.0,
      "end_time": 234400.0,
      "text": "from 70 dollars down to about 40 dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235200.0,
      "end_time": 237136.0,
      "text": "Observability has been used to do things"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 237160.0,
      "end_time": 239816.0,
      "text": "like get people to donate blood more frequently"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 239840.0,
      "end_time": 242816.0,
      "text": "by listing the names of donors on local newsletters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 242840.0,
      "end_time": 244480.0,
      "text": "or to pay their taxes on time"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 245440.0,
      "end_time": 248256.0,
      "text": "by listing the names of delinquents on a public website."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 248280.0,
      "end_time": 250120.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 252200.0,
      "end_time": 253399.0,
      "text": "What about this example?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 254560.0,
      "end_time": 258616.0,
      "text": "Toyota got hundreds of thousands of people to buy a more fuel-efficient car"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 258640.0,
      "end_time": 262256.0,
      "text": "by making the Prius so unique ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 262280.0,
      "end_time": 263880.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 264800.0,
      "end_time": 267480.0,
      "text": "that their good deed was observable from a mile away."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 268400.0,
      "end_time": 270856.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 270880.0,
      "end_time": 273255.0,
      "text": "Alright, so observability is great,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 273279.0,
      "end_time": 276816.0,
      "text": "but we all know, we&#39;ve all seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 276840.0,
      "end_time": 279000.0,
      "text": "people walk by an opportunity to do good."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 280800.0,
      "end_time": 283376.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ll see somebody asking for money on the sidewalk"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 283400.0,
      "end_time": 286150.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ll pull out their phones and look really busy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 286400.0,
      "end_time": 289600.0,
      "text": "or they&#39;ll go to the museum and they&#39;ll waltz right on by the donation box."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 290320.0,
      "end_time": 292416.0,
      "text": "Imagine it&#39;s the holiday season"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 292440.0,
      "end_time": 296136.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re going to the supermarket, and there&#39;s a Salvation Army volunteer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 296160.0,
      "end_time": 297416.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s ringing his bell."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 297440.0,
      "end_time": 299416.0,
      "text": "A few years ago, researchers in San Diego"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 299440.0,
      "end_time": 302896.0,
      "text": "teamed up with a local chapter from the Salvation Army"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 302920.0,
      "end_time": 305120.0,
      "text": "to try to find ways to increase donations."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 306240.0,
      "end_time": 307860.0,
      "text": "What they found was kind of funny."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 308680.0,
      "end_time": 311800.0,
      "text": "When the volunteer stood in front of just one door,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 312400.0,
      "end_time": 314600.0,
      "text": "people would avoid giving by going out the other door."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 316880.0,
      "end_time": 318800.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 319800.0,
      "end_time": 322776.0,
      "text": "Well, because they can always claim, \"Oh, I didn&#39;t see the volunteer,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 322800.0,
      "end_time": 325560.0,
      "text": "or, \"I wanted to get something from over there,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 325800.0,
      "end_time": 326479.0,
      "text": "or, \"That&#39;s where my car is.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 327560.0,
      "end_time": 329480.0,
      "text": "In other words, there&#39;s lots of excuses."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 330640.0,
      "end_time": 333616.0,
      "text": "And that brings us to the second item on our checklist:"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 333640.0,
      "end_time": 335360.0,
      "text": "to eliminate excuses."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 336800.0,
      "end_time": 338456.0,
      "text": "In the case of the Salvation Army,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 338480.0,
      "end_time": 341736.0,
      "text": "eliminating excuses just means standing in front of both doors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 341760.0,
      "end_time": 343816.0,
      "text": "and sure enough, when they did this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 343840.0,
      "end_time": 345390.0,
      "text": "donations rose."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 347280.0,
      "end_time": 349455.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s when things got kind of funny,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 349480.0,
      "end_time": 350680.0,
      "text": "even funnier."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 351960.0,
      "end_time": 354496.0,
      "text": "The researchers were out in the parking lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 354520.0,
      "end_time": 357695.0,
      "text": "and they were counting people as they came in and out of the store,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 357720.0,
      "end_time": 361536.0,
      "text": "and they noticed that when the volunteers stood in front of both doors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 361560.0,
      "end_time": 363736.0,
      "text": "people stopped coming out of the store at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 363760.0,
      "end_time": 366816.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 366840.0,
      "end_time": 370976.0,
      "text": "Obviously, they were surprised by this, so they decided to look into it further,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 371000.0,
      "end_time": 376960.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s when they found that there was actually a third, smaller utility door"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 376120.0,
      "end_time": 378960.0,
      "text": "usually used to take out the recycling --"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 378120.0,
      "end_time": 379656.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 379680.0,
      "end_time": 383176.0,
      "text": "and now people were going out that door in order to avoid the volunteers."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 383200.0,
      "end_time": 385560.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 386320.0,
      "end_time": 388640.0,
      "text": "This teaches us an important lesson though."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 390480.0,
      "end_time": 394160.0,
      "text": "When we&#39;re trying to eliminate excuses, we need to be very thorough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 394400.0,
      "end_time": 396416.0,
      "text": "because people are really creative in making them."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 396440.0,
      "end_time": 398640.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 401760.0,
      "end_time": 403616.0,
      "text": "Alright, I want to switch to a setting"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 403640.0,
      "end_time": 405840.0,
      "text": "where excuses can have deadly consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 408160.0,
      "end_time": 411880.0,
      "text": "What if I told you that the world&#39;s deadliest infectious disease has a cure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 412960.0,
      "end_time": 415895.0,
      "text": "in fact, that it&#39;s had one for 70 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 415920.0,
      "end_time": 418120.0,
      "text": "a good one, one that works almost every time?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 419920.0,
      "end_time": 421480.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s incredible, but it&#39;s true."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 422400.0,
      "end_time": 424376.0,
      "text": "The disease is tuberculosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 424400.0,
      "end_time": 426695.0,
      "text": "It infects some 10 million people a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 426720.0,
      "end_time": 428840.0,
      "text": "and it kills almost two million of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 429680.0,
      "end_time": 433736.0,
      "text": "Like the blackout prevention program, we&#39;ve got the solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 433760.0,
      "end_time": 435000.0,
      "text": "The problem is people."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 436000.0,
      "end_time": 437736.0,
      "text": "People need to take their medication"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 437760.0,
      "end_time": 439656.0,
      "text": "so that they&#39;re cured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 439680.0,
      "end_time": 441840.0,
      "text": "and so that they don&#39;t get other people sick."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 443520.0,
      "end_time": 445656.0,
      "text": "For a few years now, we&#39;ve been collaborating"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 445680.0,
      "end_time": 447976.0,
      "text": "with a mobile health startup called Keheala"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 448000.0,
      "end_time": 450680.0,
      "text": "to support TB patients as they undergo treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 451280.0,
      "end_time": 454376.0,
      "text": "Now, you have to understand, TB treatment, it&#39;s really tough."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 454400.0,
      "end_time": 456976.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re talking about taking a really strong antibiotic"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 457000.0,
      "end_time": 459336.0,
      "text": "every single day for six months or more."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 459360.0,
      "end_time": 462256.0,
      "text": "That antibiotic is so strong that it will make you feel sick."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 462280.0,
      "end_time": 464256.0,
      "text": "It will make you feel nauseous and dizzy."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 464280.0,
      "end_time": 466200.0,
      "text": "It will make your pee turn funny colors."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 466720.0,
      "end_time": 469616.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also a problem because you have to go back to the clinic"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 469640.0,
      "end_time": 472560.0,
      "text": "about every week in order to get more pills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 472800.0,
      "end_time": 475536.0,
      "text": "and in sub-Saharan Africa or other places where TB is common,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 475560.0,
      "end_time": 478160.0,
      "text": "now you&#39;re talking about going someplace pretty far,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 478400.0,
      "end_time": 481560.0,
      "text": "taking tough and slow public transport,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 481800.0,
      "end_time": 483135.0,
      "text": "maybe the clinic is inefficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 483160.0,
      "end_time": 486376.0,
      "text": "So now you&#39;re talking about taking a half day off of work every week"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 486400.0,
      "end_time": 489280.0,
      "text": "from a job you desperately can&#39;t afford to lose."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 489920.0,
      "end_time": 493416.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s even worse when you consider the fact that there&#39;s a terrible stigma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 493440.0,
      "end_time": 496856.0,
      "text": "and you desperately don&#39;t want people to find that you have the disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 496880.0,
      "end_time": 499736.0,
      "text": "Some of the toughest stories we hear are actually from women"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 499760.0,
      "end_time": 503296.0,
      "text": "who, in these places where domestic violence can be kind of common,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 503320.0,
      "end_time": 506560.0,
      "text": "they tell us that they have to hide it from their husbands"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 506800.0,
      "end_time": 507719.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;re coming to the clinic."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 509800.0,
      "end_time": 512600.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s no surprise that people don&#39;t complete treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 513840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515976.00000000006,
      "text": "Can our approach really help them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 516000.0,
      "end_time": 517880.0,
      "text": "Can we really get them to stick it out?"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 520390.0,
      "end_time": 521240.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 522799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 526176.0,
      "text": "Every day, we text patients to remind them to take their medication,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 526200.0,
      "end_time": 527736.0,
      "text": "but if we stopped there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 527760.0,
      "end_time": 529816.0,
      "text": "there&#39;d be lots of excuses."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 529840.0,
      "end_time": 531296.0,
      "text": "\"Well, I didn&#39;t see the text.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 531320.0,
      "end_time": 534150.0,
      "text": "Or, \"You know, I saw the text, but then I totally forgot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 534390.0,
      "end_time": 536256.0,
      "text": "put the phone down and I just forgot about it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 536280.0,
      "end_time": 538790.0,
      "text": "Or, \"I lent the phone out to my mom.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 539600.0,
      "end_time": 541616.0,
      "text": "We have to eliminate these excuses"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 541640.0,
      "end_time": 543656.0,
      "text": "and we do that by asking patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 543680.0,
      "end_time": 546640.0,
      "text": "to log in and verify that they&#39;ve taken their medication."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 547680.0,
      "end_time": 549935.0,
      "text": "If they don&#39;t log in, we text them again."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 549960.0,
      "end_time": 552560.0,
      "text": "If they don&#39;t log in, we text them yet again."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 552880.0,
      "end_time": 556960.0,
      "text": "If, after three times, they still haven&#39;t verified,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 556120.0,
      "end_time": 557936.0,
      "text": "we notify a team of supporters"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 557960.0,
      "end_time": 560216.0,
      "text": "and that team will call and text them"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 560240.0,
      "end_time": 562400.0,
      "text": "to try to get them back on the wagon."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 562960.0,
      "end_time": 564160.0,
      "text": "No excuses."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 565520.0,
      "end_time": 569295.0,
      "text": "Our approach, which, admittedly, uses all sorts of behavioral techniques,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 569320.0,
      "end_time": 572536.0,
      "text": "including, as you&#39;ve probably noticed, observability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 572560.0,
      "end_time": 573800.0,
      "text": "it was very effective."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 574800.0,
      "end_time": 576976.0,
      "text": "Patients without access to our platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 577000.0,
      "end_time": 580160.0,
      "text": "were three times more likely not to complete treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 583520.0,
      "end_time": 584896.0,
      "text": "Alright,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 584920.0,
      "end_time": 586455.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve increased observability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 586480.0,
      "end_time": 588696.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve eliminated excuses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 588720.0,
      "end_time": 591360.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s still a third thing you need to be aware of."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 592800.0,
      "end_time": 596550.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;ve been to Washington, DC or Japan or London,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 596800.0,
      "end_time": 597776.0,
      "text": "you know that metro riders there"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 597800.0,
      "end_time": 601256.0,
      "text": "will be very careful to stand on the right-hand side of the escalator"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 601280.0,
      "end_time": 603199.0,
      "text": "so that people can go by on the left."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 604160.0,
      "end_time": 606536.0,
      "text": "But unfortunately, not everywhere is that the norm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 606560.0,
      "end_time": 609736.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s plenty of places where you can just stand on both sides"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 609760.0,
      "end_time": 611160.0,
      "text": "and block the escalator."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 611400.0,
      "end_time": 612656.0,
      "text": "Obviously, it&#39;s better for others"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 612680.0,
      "end_time": 614976.0,
      "text": "when we stand on the right and let them go by,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 615000.0,
      "end_time": 617720.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;re only expected to do that some places."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 618720.0,
      "end_time": 620136.0,
      "text": "This is a general phenomenon."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 620160.0,
      "end_time": 622216.0,
      "text": "Sometimes we&#39;re expected to do good"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 622240.0,
      "end_time": 624560.0,
      "text": "and sometimes not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 624800.0,
      "end_time": 627456.0,
      "text": "and it means that people are really sensitive to cues"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 627480.0,
      "end_time": 630440.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;re expected to do good in a particular situation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 631600.0,
      "end_time": 635296.0,
      "text": "which brings us to the third and final item on our checklist:"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 635320.0,
      "end_time": 637960.0,
      "text": "to communicate expectations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 637120.0,
      "end_time": 638536.0,
      "text": "to tell people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 638560.0,
      "end_time": 640640.0,
      "text": "\"Do the good deed right now.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 642680.0,
      "end_time": 644935.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a simple way to communicate expectations;"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 644960.0,
      "end_time": 648136.0,
      "text": "simply tell them, \"Hey, everybody else is doing the good deed.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 648160.0,
      "end_time": 652336.0,
      "text": "The company Opower sends people in their electricity bill"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 652360.0,
      "end_time": 655136.0,
      "text": "a small insert that compares their energy consumption"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 655160.0,
      "end_time": 658400.0,
      "text": "with that of people with similarly sized homes."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 659000.0,
      "end_time": 662456.0,
      "text": "And when people find out that their neighbors are using less electricity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 662480.0,
      "end_time": 664376.0,
      "text": "they start to consume less."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 664400.0,
      "end_time": 668550.0,
      "text": "That same approach, it&#39;s been used to get people to vote or give to charity"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 668800.0,
      "end_time": 670200.0,
      "text": "or even reuse their towels in hotels."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 672240.0,
      "end_time": 673440.0,
      "text": "What about this one?"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 674240.0,
      "end_time": 676736.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s another way to communicate expectations;"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 676760.0,
      "end_time": 680840.0,
      "text": "simply do it by saying, \"Do the good deed\" just at the right time."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 683840.0,
      "end_time": 685400.0,
      "text": "What about this one?"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 686320.0,
      "end_time": 688936.0,
      "text": "This ticker reframes"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 688960.0,
      "end_time": 691776.0,
      "text": "the kind of mundane task of turning off the lights"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 691800.0,
      "end_time": 694640.0,
      "text": "and turns it instead into an environmental contribution."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 696320.0,
      "end_time": 699136.0,
      "text": "The bottom line is, lots of different ways to do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 699160.0,
      "end_time": 701216.0,
      "text": "lots of ways to communicate expectations."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 701240.0,
      "end_time": 702526.0,
      "text": "Just don&#39;t forget to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 703320.0,
      "end_time": 704616.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s it."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 704640.0,
      "end_time": 705840.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s our checklist."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 708440.0,
      "end_time": 712776.0,
      "text": "Many of you are working on problems with important social consequences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 712800.0,
      "end_time": 716199.0,
      "text": "and sometimes you might need to motivate people to do more good."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 717520.0,
      "end_time": 720536.0,
      "text": "The tools you learned today can help you with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 720560.0,
      "end_time": 723736.0,
      "text": "And these tools, they don&#39;t require that you raise additional funds"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 723760.0,
      "end_time": 726656.0,
      "text": "or that you develop any more fancy technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 726680.0,
      "end_time": 729455.0,
      "text": "They just require harnessing reputations"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 729480.0,
      "end_time": 732896.0,
      "text": "by increasing observability, eliminating excuses"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 732920.0,
      "end_time": 734520.0,
      "text": "and communicating expectations."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 736120.0,
      "end_time": 737336.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 737360.0,
      "end_time": 741800.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}